title: Searching Good Thresh mains for DuoQ.
body:
I was Gold 3 this season, but after a period got full feeder teams. 
And by maining adc, you can't carry 1v9, versus fed Fioras and Le Blancs.
So i wondered if i could have a better support that can duoq with me and actually help me carry 2v8 :D.
If you type your summonernames down it would be awesome. (not only Thresh mains)

replies.body: Why an english player seek people in italian forum?
Maybe because i live in Italy? {{sticker:slayer-jinx-catface}}
